&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://papertrailapp.com/&quot;&gt;Papertrail&lt;/a&gt; provides log management as a service. We work with tens of thousands of ops-savvy developers, systems engineers, and entrepreneurs at companies like GitHub, Heroku, Instacart, Adobe, and DNSimple.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;That&#39;s where you come in. We&#39;ve grown to need technical customer support to help customers make the most of Papertrail. Here&#39;s a few examples of what customers think of Papertrail&#39;s support:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TiuTalk/status/714592766827872257&quot;&gt;https://twitter.com/TiuTalk/status/714592766827872257&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/agmakonts/status/730356796607614976&quot;&gt;https://twitter.com/agmakonts/status/730356796607614976&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/hectcastro/status/717523363032391680&quot;&gt;https://twitter.com/hectcastro/status/717523363032391680&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Summary&lt;/h2&gt;
