&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Okay, cool. What&#39;s involved?&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Help customers setup and use Papertrail&#39;s service in email and text chat. The questions are about a wide range of topics like Linux, syslog, Web framework logging, Ruby, Rails, IP stack troubleshooting, PHP, REST/JSON, Python, firewall rules, Node.js, plus non-technical topics.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You almost certainly won&#39;t know about all of these. While a strong working knowledge of Linux is required, Googling to satisfy your own curiosity is a lot more valuable (and hopefully, fun). Also:&lt;/p&gt;
